  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This trial aims to investigate whether tailored lifestyle consultation through SNP testing
      leads to more effective weight loss among overweight or obese individuals compared to general
      lifestyle guidance for weight control.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
